        <scopecontent id="ref3">
            <head>Scope and Contents note</head>
            <p>This collection contains miscellaneous and unrelated meteorological observations from the mid-18th Century to the early 19th Century profiling locations as diverse as Philadelphia, South America, and London. The majority of the records contain daily charts noting the prominent weather indicators, some of which include remarks by the respective authors.</p>
        </scopecontent>
